Layout<T>
public class SpringLayout<T>
extends AbstractLayout<T>

SpringLayout assigns X/Y locations to each node. When called, the it moves the visualization forward one step.

Author:
Danyel Fisher, Joshua O'Madadhain, Sabina Sara Pfister - adaptation for Cytoscape
